data.description: Welcome to your dream coastal getaway! This charming 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom cottage has been newly renovated to offer the perfect blend of comfort and style. With its light and bright interior, shiplap accent walls, and an open-concept layout, you'll find it hard to resist the coastal charmer. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The newly renovated kitchen is a highlight. Every corner of this cottage has been thoughtfully designed to make you feel at home. Outside, a fully fenced yard provides privacy and a secure space for your furry friends to roam. Located on the desirable West End, you'll enjoy the tranquility of the coastal setting while being just minutes away from Galveston attractions, and the beautiful beach. This cozy coastal cottage is the perfect oasis for full-time living, a weekend retreat, or an investment property. Your coastal dream begins here, where comfort and style meet seaside living.
